title: "MCP TOOL_SCHEMA_BASE additionalProperties:true silently swallows typo'd top-level args"
description: "All narrow tool schemas inherit additionalProperties:true; a typo like fullChangedField (missing s) is ignored with no error, so agents silently get default behavior."
